# Useful Shortcuts

| Command       | Description                 |
| ------------- | --------------------------- |
| `ng s`        | Start Development Server    |
| `ng s -o`     | Start Server & Open Browser |
| `ng g c`      | Generate Component          |
| `ng g s`      | Generate Service            |
| `ng build`    | Build Project               |
| `ng test`     | Run Unit Tests              |
| `ng version`  | Check Angular Version       |
| `npm install` | Install Dependencies        |

